title: Make Her Want You Texting Secrets - Part 2 (Episode 190)
description:
Show Notes:

In this episode you'll get special inside access to our "Texting Guide" and real life examples of how to apply the concepts and theories to optimize your dating funnel...

What to do if she's late to your date... [01:47]
How to follow up after a date? [03:30]
The critical thing you must avoid if you're using specific texting examples... [04:04]
How to stay top of mind when you're not sure when you'll be able to see her next... [09:33]
What to text after sex... [18:00]
Robbie's crazy story about a girl who was really hard to make plans with even though the sex was great... [21:20]
Dealing with non-committal women... [25:47]
What to do if she flakes... [35:10]
The exception to the flake (when she's telling the truth)... [38:40]
How to handle the situation where she's wishy washy or slightly resistant last second to meeting... [42:15]
Not sure if you're in the let's just be friends zone, here's a text you can send to find out... [44:33]
The best way to get out of the friend zone...? [45:29]
How to optimally use the "Cool Story Bro" epic text... [48:37]
How to play offense with memes and the "Cock Pic Windup"... [49:30]
What to do if she stops responding... [53:20]
What over-investing looks like, a cringey example... [55:33]
What to do if she doesn't remember your name? [57:20]
What to text if you got her number but didn't have enough time to make a solid connection... [1:01:27]

Links:
Learn more from this texting guide - www.innerconfidence.com/texting
